summary: This is Scodia, the first character I made in skyrim and i think she looks gorgeous. Their are only a few redguard female saves
descriptionHtml:
This is a saved game file for my a character I have created named Scodia, She is a redguard female. I think she\'s pretty cute, The file will drop you off just before your first choice in Helgen. Whether you go with the imperial or the Stormcloaks.

There has been no other things added apart from my customisation to the apperance she\'s vanilla.

Screenshots show one of her in vanilla settings without mods, and the others are the much improved textures via mods on this site which make he looks even nicer.

Extract file and move to C:\\Users\\-USERNAME-\\Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves

If done correctly you will be able to load game from start menu of skyrim

Thanks for downloading.
author: Scodia
